173
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:34,400
Are you fine spending your years
behind bars alone?

174
00:14:34,570 --> 00:14:36,600
That jerk will walk freely.

175
00:14:38,570 --> 00:14:41,880
Who are you? A fuzz?

176
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:44,350
A fuzz?

177
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:48,650
