And you're threatening me?

183
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:17,240
Goodness, I'm scared.

184
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:20,510
Hey, look here!
These people are threatening me!

185
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:23,850
Is this even possible
in a democratic society in Korea?

186
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:26,250
-Calm down.
-He's about to hit me!

187
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:32,990
Get lost! I did all I had to do!

188
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:37,800
If you dare touch a single strand
of my family's hair,

189
