Hello, ma'am.

205
00:17:08,460 --> 00:17:11,890
The woman
who bought conch abalone porridge.

206
00:17:11,990 --> 00:17:13,430
What about her?

207
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:15,260
Do you know where she went?

208
00:17:15,329 --> 00:17:16,800
I haven't seen her at the market either.

209
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:18,730
I don't know either.

210
00:17:19,369 --> 00:17:21,839
