241
00:18:52,530 --> 00:18:53,830
Did you get into a fight?

242
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:58,170
-Well, you know.
-Detective Gu looked the same.

243
00:18:59,530 --> 00:19:01,870
Then what's with your arm?

244
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:03,800
Did you work out or what?

245
00:19:03,870 --> 00:19:06,210
