Talking made me even more hungry!

248
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:17,280
Seems like there's a lot over there.

249
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,420
Let's go.

250
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:20,450
Is it a sashimi place?

251
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:25,360
I wonder what's good here.

252
00:19:28,030 --> 00:19:29,060
Let's toast.

253
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,980
May I ask you something?

254
00:19:43,840 --> 00:19:45,980
That man, An Ji-yong.

255
00:19:47,010 --> 00:19:49,250
Why is he going this far?

256
00:19:50,580 --> 00:19:53,120
Going as far as killing someone
who's in the hospital bed.

257
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:57,090
If Chairman Hwang Na-yoon passes away,

258
00:19:57,790 --> 00:20:00,660
all the inheritance rights
go to the legal spouse.

259
00:20:01,530 --> 00:20:03,530
In Hong Kong,

260
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:05,830
he lived as Hwang Na-yoon's husband,

261
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:09,170
Kevin Hwang.

262
00:20:11,410 --> 00:20:13,210
He ordered Chairman Hwang Na-yoon

263
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:15,710
to siphon the foundation funds
to the Hong Kong account.

264
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:18,850
Now that she passed away,

265
00:20:19,810 --> 00:20:21,620
he's trying to transfer
those funds as he pleases.

266
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:24,990
He's no human.

267
00:20:26,490 --> 00:20:27,920
