415
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:44,940
[They don't sell them here yet.]

416
00:30:45,340 --> 00:30:47,840
[But Jun-hee and Tommy have them.]

417
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:51,580
Si-woo, I...

418
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,750
[Mom, what's wrong?]

419
00:30:54,050 --> 00:30:56,080
[-Are you crying?]
-No.

420
00:31:02,090 --> 00:31:03,290
I'm sorry, Si-woo.

421
00:31:04,990 --> 00:31:06,090
I...

422
00:31:08,190 --> 00:31:11,460
I really wanted to do a good job
this time.

423
00:31:12,370 --> 00:31:13,470
