428
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:22,980
[I'm okay with it.]

429
00:31:23,110 --> 00:31:26,910
[So stop crying and don't forget
to get cards on your way back, okay?]

430
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,820
