474
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:23,590
then the one billion dollar investment
must be returned.

475
00:34:27,989 --> 00:34:28,929
Okay.

476
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,960
I want to make a decision.

477
00:34:32,530 --> 00:34:36,139
If you're against it,
state your position now.

478
00:34:40,270 --> 00:34:43,380
I am Nam Ji-seon.
I represent the parents of the PTA.

479
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:47,280
All of this is being discussed

480
00:34:47,380 --> 00:34:49,420
without the parents' opinion or consent,

481
00:34:49,480 --> 00:34:51,719
and I can't take it anymore.

