and the legal representative.

494
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:29,790
Right, I will take full responsibility
for everything.

495
00:35:31,990 --> 00:35:34,760
[If the foundation continues
to make decisions without our consent,]

496
00:35:34,830 --> 00:35:36,360
we, as parents,

497
00:35:36,430 --> 00:35:38,430
