648
00:45:18,940 --> 00:45:21,050
No matter how much money
has been transferred.

649
00:45:21,110 --> 00:45:23,520
So you decided that by yourself
and invalidated it?

650
00:45:23,650 --> 00:45:25,050
It wasn't by myself.

651
00:45:25,550 --> 00:45:28,720
I did it as the legal advisor
of the HSC school foundation

652
00:45:29,120 --> 00:45:31,520
on behalf of Chairman Hwang Na-yoon.

653
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:33,230
I have the authority to process it

654
00:45:33,290 --> 00:45:34,860
according to the procedures
and regulations.

655
00:45:35,690 --> 00:45:38,430
And President Nam Ji-seon,

656
00:45:38,730 --> 00:45:41,570
you also had a big stake
in that illegal transaction.

657
00:45:43,870 --> 00:45:45,270
I told you before, didn't I?

658
00:45:46,110 --> 00:45:47,740
That I'd figure everything out one day.

659
00:45:48,610 --> 00:45:50,210
Your relationship
with my husband An Ji-yong

660
00:45:50,310 --> 00:45:52,610
and the school foundation.

661
00:45:54,350 --> 00:45:56,520
Pretending to be for the school
and the children,

662
00:45:57,020 --> 00:45:59,550
you've been washing money very exquisitely

663
00:45:59,820 --> 00:46:01,790
by connecting the foundation
and the hotel.

664
00:46:04,920 --> 00:46:08,090
You seem very proud
of what you've discovered.

665
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:10,700
But that's barely anything.

666
00:46:11,200 --> 00:46:13,430
All I did was my best

667
00:46:13,700 --> 00:46:15,600
for this school and the children.

668
00:46:15,670 --> 00:46:17,870
Can you even imagine?

669
00:46:17,940 --> 00:46:20,310
What the school would be like
if it weren't for me?

670
00:46:20,470 --> 00:46:21,610
The best...

671
00:46:22,140 --> 00:46:24,780
That doesn't justify what you've done.

672
00:46:27,010 --> 00:46:30,250
President Nam Ji-seon,
on behalf of the HSC Foundation,

673
00:46:30,320 --> 00:46:33,290
I accuse you of breach of trust
and embezzlement.

674
00:46:35,590 --> 00:46:37,020
It's really your turn now.

675
00:46:37,220 --> 00:46:38,860
You won't be able
to escape from it anymore.

676
00:46:41,460 --> 00:46:43,800
How dare you mess around with me?

677
00:46:44,300 --> 00:46:45,830
You're nothing but a mere lawyer.

678
00:46:46,830 --> 00:46:49,800
You must be thinking
you're practicing great justice,

679
00:46:50,200 --> 00:46:52,300
but why don't you look back on yourself?

680
00:46:52,670 --> 00:46:54,610
Your husband and child.

681
00:46:54,670 --> 00:46:56,140
Do you think you have the right?

682
00:47:00,710 --> 00:47:04,020
Even if it's late,

683
00:47:04,380 --> 00:47:07,390
I'm at least trying to fix what's wrong.

684
00:47:08,420 --> 00:47:10,690
But what about you?

685
00:47:12,490 --> 00:47:15,090
But you're pathetic until the very end.

686
00:47:39,050 --> 00:47:40,990
President.

687
00:47:41,120 --> 00:47:42,890
I'm not in the mood to talk right now,
so get out.

688
00:47:43,920 --> 00:47:46,630
Director Lee didn't show up
at the hospital in Seoul

689
00:47:46,790 --> 00:47:48,330
and nobody can get in touch
with him the whole day.

690
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:51,100
What do you mean?

691
00:47:52,000 --> 00:47:55,130
-What about Nurse Bang?
-He dropped him off at the hospital,

692
00:47:55,400 --> 00:47:56,870
