00:50:42,570 --> 00:50:44,840
I'm quite a busy man as well.

721
00:50:45,070 --> 00:50:46,540
Where are you right now?

722
00:50:48,270 --> 00:50:50,210
What?

723
00:50:52,840 --> 00:50:55,050
