00:55:01,360 --> 00:55:02,330
What?

768
00:56:02,290 --> 00:56:03,420
It's been a while.

769
00:56:15,230 --> 00:56:16,670
What are you doing?

770
00:56:16,800 --> 00:56:19,770
Calm down. You wanted to meet me alone.

771
00:56:31,150 --> 00:56:32,280
Aren't you happy to see me?

772
00:56:33,550 --> 00:56:35,450
Are you so surprised?

773
00:56:38,690 --> 00:56:39,790
You look like

774
00:56:40,590 --> 00:56:42,860
you're angry that I'm still alive.

775
00:56:48,870 --> 00:56:49,930
You

776
00:56:51,670 --> 00:56:53,840
abandoned me and Yi-chan completely.

777
00:56:54,640 --> 00:56:56,310
You turned

778
00:56:57,510 --> 00:56:59,410
the time we spent together into a lie.

779
00:57:00,710 --> 00:57:02,380
