780
00:57:02,810 --> 00:57:03,980
I had to save myself first.

781
00:57:04,050 --> 00:57:05,750
You could've told me.

782
00:57:05,820 --> 00:57:08,450
I told you to trust me and wait.

783
00:57:08,820 --> 00:57:10,490
